<concept id="id9yz-09126-ug01-pczza-sp1-d1e195392"><title>Time of Day and Day of Week</title><conbody>
<section><title>Overview</title>
<p>The time of day and day of week functionality allows operators to apply special tariff plans based on the specific time and day. Operators can use <uicontrol>Time-Of-Day</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Day-Of-Week</uicontrol> parameters in the <userinput>CALL_COMMON</userinput> source context in the rules to configure this feature. </p>
